            <img src="img/feature-4.png">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="span6 txt-right feature-desc">
        <h2>Responsive Layouts</h2>
        <p>
            The Sample pages and the store are built by taking a mobile first approach. It works in your tablet and your phone as good as in your browser. This enables you to access your favorite gadgets, engage with your users and handle your business from wherever you are.
        </p>
    </div>

</div>

